data.description:
*Sellers are offering up to 3% towards closing cost!!
Close to everything that Jarrell has to offer, and with the added bonus of a short commute to concentrations of employment, the "location, location, location" advantages of this captivating 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom Traditional are enough to earn a spot at the top of your list! Come enjoy luxurious living in Sonterra, the desirable development in Jarrell. From its position on a quiet, low-traffic street, the home is only a short distance to the oasis of nature that is Georgetown Lake and Salado Creek. The immediate neighborhood is free from the bustle of commercial districts, while also being within pedestrian range of Jarrell ISD. This home offers a treasure they say money can't buy: extra time, afforded by the painless commute to concentrations of employment. This appealing dwelling is a great opportunity in the Sonterra development.  Enjoy the large granite counter space with the open view to the living area.  So much to love about the calm main-floor spacious master bedroom that includes a large walk-in closet, double vanity and walk in shower. The other three bedrooms, offering the convenience of main-floor accessibility, are quiet and ready for your decorative touch. Attached two-car garage and spacious attic. Exterior includes an inviting patio and a breezy back porch. Open the front door to a pleasant new life here in Jarrell.
